values:
I now have a ujournal. 
Im still going to use this one.
But my ujournal is 100x cooler looking.
So anyone with a ujournal add me up.

I just got back from the hospital like an hour ago. It turns out my dad has broken ribs and a puntured lung. And his face is really fucked up.

I just thought Id update.

Today was a horrible day.

Im sitting in third hour and Mr. Woodley tells me to go to the office and to take all my stuff.

So I walk down there thinking that it was about classes next year or something and my cousin is there and all she says is your going home.

I come home and find out the my dad got into a bad motorcycle accident on his way to Washington.

He was in Taylor getting ready to go and some jackass ran a red light and hit him and took off. His motorcycle is totaled and he is in the hospital. They know for sure he broke all his ribs but they are still running test to make sure everything else is ok.

And the worst part is the asshole who hit him didnt even stop to make sure he was ok, he just took off.

 

Hopefully Ill get to go seem him in a bit. Ill probably end up staying with him for a while after this one..

I cant believe that school is almost over.

Thats both awsome and terrifying at the same time.

Im gonna be a junior next year.
That means only 2 years till Im 18 off to college and on my own. And thats not a good thing seein as how I pretty much wasted sophmore year acting like a dick and not doing what I needed to.

I really need to step it up and prove myself next year.
I want anyone and everyone who reads this to post in here something they would like to do with me someday. Then post this in your journal to find out what I want to do with you.

Blink concert was rather disappointing.
It sucks when one of your favorite bands is a tremendous letdown.
I dont really feel like writing.
I just thought Id share that with you though.


[Post Script]: Straylight Run is now officially one of my favorite bands. Exsistentialism on Prom Night - One of the best songs ever written.

Last night was the funnest, craziest, most adventurous night Ive had in quite some time.

The day starts with school.
What a drag.
But after school I went to scotts and we chilled untill we left for the concert.
On the way there I was flashing other motorists with my man boobies. It was quite amusing.
The show was amazing. Dashboard Confessional was...Orgasmic thats the only way to describe their performance. 
After the show we are driving home and scott was like I have to take a shit.
Yeah, So we went to his dads store in D-Town so he could poo.
But when he comes out of the bathroom he gets like really sick all the sudden and his lips swell up about 4x bigger than they should be. 
So he takes a shower to see if that would help. And we leave.
On the way home we run into torrential rains.
Every road is flooded and- oh my scotts dads car stalls.
And It wouldnt start for over an hour. 
Me and Bobby had to go out into the rain and the water flooded up to my knee and push the car to some little convience store.
Where it still wouldnt start for a half hour.
It was kinda fun playin in the rain though.
So I didnt end up getting home untill 2:30 and then gettin to bed untill 3:00 cause I had to eat something.
The upside is my mom let me skip school :) .

Blink 182, Taking Back Sunday, and The Used is tonight. I can only imagine what adventures this one will bring.


Im going to go call scott and see if he went to school or not.

-The only broken hearted loser...




(P.S. I got a Security guard named Tiffany to autograph my chest. It was awsome. haha.)

I guess Ill update this.
I dont really want to.
But Sarah told me to so I will.
Today was boring.
The school was like empty because of Senior Skip Day.
Lunch was fun.
But Sarah punched me in the face AND made me cut my arm.
Geeze.
For no reason to.
Anyways now im just sitting here bored as hell.
Nothing to do.
Noone to hang out with.


Dashboard Confeesional, Thrice, & The Get Up Kids--6 Days
Blink 182, T.B.S., and The Used --7 Days


Maybe Ill write more later maybe not.

I need to get the fuck out of here.

I hate every aspect of my life.

 

 

 

I FUCKING LOSE

I hate this.
I wish everything was ok.
But its not.
It sucks when people dont turn out to be who you thought they were.
It sucks even more when you lose the people you care most about.



It's so nice sitting very still,
in a room where no one else can feel the pain that breaks my heart each day, I'm not ok.
Sunlight shining through my window, let's me know that I'm still alive
Why did I ever let you inside my heart? I'm such a fool.
Paint my face in shades of blood and grey and take a seat right next to me
Well I should've known that you were a killer.
But now I'm dead.

A gaping hole, shot through my heart
A lost connection from your poison dart
Shot from your tounge to end my life.
You're blowing at the fire to light your strife.

You'll never know.
The hardest thing about dying is, knowing you'll never see the light of day.

A gaping hole shot...(shot through my heart)
A lost connection from your poison dart.
My head now spins and my ears bleed gold.
I try so fucking hard, but I can't fit your mold.

You ripped my heart out, you tore my eyes out, now you're gonna pay
I'll stab you one time.
I'll eat your heart out so you feel my pain.
Don't you know that I always see you in all of my dreams?
I wanna kill you. I wanna kill you. Now i'm insane.



















Ive just got to accept it.
The time we spent was great.
Too bad we couldnt have had something more.
Goodbye, My love.

Lyrics are good.
Oh yes, lyrics a grand.
Especially when they mean something to you.



Last night I had a dream that we went to Disneyland, Went on all the rides, didn't have to wait in line. I drove you to your house where we stared up at the stars I listened to your heartbeat as I held you in my arms. We hung out at the rainbow where we drank til' half past two. Nothing could go wrong anytime that I'm with you. Like crashing a hotel room or leading up to that first kiss Or searching for a high school that you know doesn't exist... These are the things that make me free I feel like I'm stuck in "stand by me" This night was too good to be true. Today I woke up alone wishing you were here with me, I wanted us to be something that we'd probably never be. Today you called me up and said you'd see me at our show, But now I'm stuck debating if I even wanna go. Whitney, don't you understand that what I say is true? I just want you to know I have a major crush on you. I'd drive you to Las Vegas and do the things you wanna do I'd even have Wayne Newton dedicate a song to you. I only wish that this could be Just dump your boyfriend and go out with me I swear I'd treat you like a queen


To hot to type. Ill update later.

Entry two.
Im on a roll here.
This weekend has been extremely mundane.
Oh well though.
I lose.
Last night was cool,
talking to some sweet people.
But not great.
It kind of made me lonely.
But again, I lose.

First entry.
This could make or break my live journal future.
Pressure is on.
Ok not really but any who..

Its funny,
The memorys and feelings a single photograph
can bring back to you.
Oh well though,
That is in the past.
I moved on a long time ago.
Im better off this way.

Didnt do much tonight
It was fun anways.
Talking to some majorly rad people
Cant go wrong there.
